<HEAD>New Miss USA Is Texas' Fifth in a Row</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserColor MOB7</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By GARRY MITCHELL</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
