esources to adequately screen immigrants. <LOCATION> Australia </LOCATION> was crying out for immigrants in the immediate post-war years and just filling the ships to bring them to <LOCATION> Australia </LOCATION>,'' which now has double the population of 16 million. <PERSON> Greenwood </PERSON> has traveled to the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Israel </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Canada </LOCATION> and <LOCATION> Britain </LOCATION> to pursue his investigations.
